'''Glen Mullaly''' is a Canadian book and magazine illustrator who co-illustrated, with [[Ken Steacy]], ''[[X-Wing Marks the Spot]]'', ''[[Imperial Spy]]'' and ''[[Podracing Tales]]'' as well as numerous Star Wars children's books for ''[[Random House]]'' and Golden Books, among others.

